nodes.text: The Tessellated Arboreal binjinphant was a very rare and furry tree-dwelling marsupial.
Ingey was the binjinphant of Coby of Tammuz-an. He was kidnapped by Starhunter's Intergalactic Menagerie on Chuzalla.

The Tessellated Arboreal binjinphant appeared in two episodes of the Star Wars Droids television series. The creature later received a mention in the online game Star Wars Galaxies, in a quest relating to the Holocron of Destiny.
